What you need to know:

At the same time, a team of five firers who will compete at the Bollard Shooting Championships due March 26-27 in South Africa, also received the national flag.Tony Karanja, Mwangi Gikonyo, Peter Njoroge, Sammy Onyango and Ibrahim Ndugu will be using the event to prepare for the national trials for the World IPSC Championships due November in the United Kingdom.